01:09:05.819 --> 01:09:11.279
On the contrary, you could
simply say, over 10,000 years,

01:09:11.279 --> 01:09:17.250
we achieved achieve more
than 400 million before us.

01:09:17.250 --> 01:09:27.050
And there's many
benefits that have come

01:09:27.050 --> 01:09:30.680
from urbanization in our time.

01:09:34.979 --> 01:09:36.780
Maybe it will continue--

01:09:36.780 --> 01:09:40.760
but hopefully, less selectively
than it's been up to now.

01:09:43.370 --> 01:09:53.300
There's no law that asks
you to be a social animal.

01:09:53.300 --> 01:09:57.290
You can't drive into
somebody else's garden

01:09:57.290 --> 01:09:59.630
and get away with it.

01:09:59.630 --> 01:10:04.170
But there's nothing
that requires

01:10:04.170 --> 01:10:10.050
you to see your own condition in
the light of other people less

01:10:10.050 --> 01:10:11.940
fortunate.

01:10:11.940 --> 01:10:14.580
Charity was invented
by the British.

01:10:14.580 --> 01:10:18.160
Well, charity has
been with us forever.

01:10:18.160 --> 01:10:21.810
But at the end of
the 19th century,

01:10:21.810 --> 01:10:28.510
charity was seen as the
major involvement of wealth.

01:10:28.510 --> 01:10:31.510
It still is in this country.

01:10:31.510 --> 01:10:36.890
I get upset every time
I get a phone call

01:10:36.890 --> 01:10:41.090
asking me to donate something
and trying to reconstruct

01:10:41.090 --> 01:10:46.700
my own ideology, which is not
in favor of charity at all,

01:10:46.700 --> 01:10:52.095
but charity being only a method
of conceding the government's

01:10:52.095 --> 01:10:52.595
inaction.

01:10:59.010 --> 01:11:01.980
There's no-- I don't know.

01:11:01.980 --> 01:11:04.340
It's very complicated.

01:11:04.340 --> 01:11:08.250
It's very fundamentally
complicated as to who was--

01:11:08.250 --> 01:11:16.410
why was I statistically
born to have enough money

01:11:16.410 --> 01:11:21.795
to come and study here and then
have enough energy to stay?

01:11:24.450 --> 01:11:26.670
I'll never be able to answer--

01:11:26.670 --> 01:11:32.070
as opposed to a child growing
up in the Congo today.

01:11:32.070 --> 01:11:37.110
What statistical right do
I have over that child?

01:11:37.110 --> 01:11:41.310
These are questions
philosophers have argued with.

01:11:41.310 --> 01:11:42.195
They may be tedious.

01:11:48.530 --> 01:11:52.040
But Marxism didn't
solve the problem.

01:11:52.040 --> 01:11:58.190
Marxism only introduced
a new form of power,

01:11:58.190 --> 01:12:03.110
despite all of the
grassroots sentiments,

01:12:03.110 --> 01:12:08.830
it didn't result in anything.

01:12:08.830 --> 01:12:11.620
OK, see you next week--

